<h2 align=center> <font color="#800000">Capital Connection <br>Looking for Small Business Financing? </h2> </font color>

<p>Find Angel investors, small business loans, venture capital funding, a 
<a href="https://www.sharestates.com">Crowdfunding Real Estate Investing</a>, business financing, and business resources and consultants. Over 1000 different resources linked from <a href="money.html">Business Financing</a> including more than 500 <a href="venturecapital.html">venture capital firms</a> and <a href="networksangels.html">angel networks</a>  Find out the truth about Grants for Businesses. Interest in <a href="https://www.sharestates.com/">multifamily investing</a> If you're looking for money for starting a business you've come to the right place. More business start-ups fail from not having enough money for business financing than any other reason. Business start-up financing is available but sometimes isn't easy to find. 

<h2 align=center> <font color="#800000">Business Plan Review <br>& Critique Service</h2></font color>
	
<P align=left>Let Us Look At Your Plan From The Investor's Point of View. <a href="writing-a-business-plan.html">Writing a Business Plan</a> for a new venture, or an ongoing business, can be a time consuming task. If you're looking for capital you can destroy your chances right off the bat. That's bad news for you and your company. An amateurish, incomplete, business plan reflects on your management team and a strong management team is the most critical factor when investors decide to invest. A poorly written plan all but disqualifies you in today's race for investors. Your business plan will be reviewed from the executive summary to the very last page.  Find out more about our <a href="business-plan-review.html">business plan review</a> services.<BR><BR>

